        {
            "title": "中國開除軍方多位高層的黨籍 反腐敗力度加大（1）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著中國國家主席習近平的反腐敗力度加大，中國已開除兩名最高級別軍事官員的黨籍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據國防部發布的聲明稱，中央軍委副主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:何衛東;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/何衛東\">何衛東</a>嚴重違反黨的紀律。他是軍委兩位副主席之一，主席為習近平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五公佈的聲明中，共有九人被黨中央決定開除黨籍處分，包括軍委政治工作部原主任苗華。四中全會將於幾天後將召開。屆時，中共高層領導人將齊聚北京，討論經濟規劃和人事調整。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聲明稱，這九人被控「嚴重違反黨的紀律」和「涉嫌嚴重職務犯罪，數額特別巨大」。國防部還補充說，「性質極為嚴重，影響極其惡劣」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bccd8fa8-8917-3eff-8fa3-3993b77c112d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">繼1989年6月趙紫陽因支持抗議學生而被撤銷軍委會副主席一職後，何衛東是30多年來第一位遭到撤換的現任軍委副主席。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">何衛東也成為自2017年原重慶市委書記孫政才遭到調查以來第一位落馬的政治局委員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">何衛東最後一次公開露面是在3月11日，當時他出席了在北京舉行的全國人大會議閉幕式。他未出席4月初的植樹活動，通常情況下，兩位軍委副主席都會出席。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Ousts Top Military Officials as Xi Widens Corruption Purge</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(全文更新)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E9%99%A4%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%A4%9A%E4%BD%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%A8%E7%B1%8D-%E5%8F%8D%E8%85%90%E6%95%97%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7-1-105217689.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 21:00:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股銀行板塊盤前延續跌勢 市場聚焦地區性銀行財報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"965\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hV.I7QOgUozIOr5mdLA1tw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8467aeb36c8bc96d80ab4171603592c8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國的銀行類股周五盤前交易中延續跌勢，此前地區性銀行股遭遇重挫，引發亞洲和歐洲交易時段的連鎖反應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至紐約時間4:40，美國銀行、花旗集團、摩根士丹利和富國銀行股價均下跌逾1.5%。此前，地區性銀行股周四大幅下挫，其中Zions Bancorp和Western Alliance Bancorp領跌，兩家機構均表示成為欺詐受害者，涉及向投資不良商業抵押貸款的基金放貸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五盤前交易時段，地區性銀行股成交量有限，但Zions股價仍下跌1.8%。周四標普地區銀行精選行業指數跌6.3%，此次拋售潮令人聯想到4月時關稅引發的暴跌，以及2023年危機期間該板塊遭受的重創。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-49947858-7117-3756-af80-f100e35a73f9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場焦點將迅速轉向該類銀行最新財報，多家大型地區性銀行將於紐約開盤前公佈業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ginjer AM執行長Leonard Cohen表示，「投資者理所當然地感到擔憂，在類似情形下總是如此，因為他們尚未識別出風險所在」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"965\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/09ocqCk7VOnC1E6BAoNA3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/181b027b211654f7e717582aaf10ea04\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Bank Stocks Rout Deepens as Investors Brace for Earnings</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Georgie McKay.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A%E7%9B%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%8C%E5%8B%A2-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%80%A7%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1-100517357.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 20:35:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
